---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="About"
    description="About Oliver Steele - Software engineer, educator, and maker"
>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About</h1>

        <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
            <section class="mb-8">
                <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    I'm a software engineer, educator, and maker passionate
                    about building tools for creativity and learning. Currently
                    a graduate student at Tsinghua SIGS in Shenzhen, China, I
                    bring experience from roles at Apple, Nest Labs, and various
                    startups, combined with academic positions at NYU Shanghai
                    and Franklin W. Olin College of Engineering.
                </p>

                <p class="mb-6">
                    My work spans from developing core technologies at companies
                    like Apple (Quickdraw GX graphics engine) and Nest (backend
                    services for the Learning Thermostat), to creating <a
                        href="/software"
                        class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                        >open-source tools and libraries</a
                    > that have inspired language features in CoffeeScript and beyond.
                    I've founded startups, led engineering teams, and hold multiple
                    patents in areas ranging from IoT systems to interactive shopping
                    experiences.
                </p>

                <p class="mb-6">
                    As an educator, I've developed and <a
                        href="/teaching/courses"
                        class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                        >taught courses</a
                    > in creative coding, physical computing, software design, and
                    <a
                        href="/woodworking"
                        class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                        >woodworking for art and design</a
                    >. My teaching philosophy centers on hands-on learning,
                    creative expression, and building tools that empower others
                    to create.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Tech Stack</h2>

                <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
                    While I've also done commercial work in Assembly, C, C++,
                    Common Lisp, Java, and with AWS and Twilio, my current
                    preferred stack includes:
                </p>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Languages</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
                            <li>TypeScript/JavaScript for web development</li>
                            <li>
                                Python for AI/ML applications and backend
                                services
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Python, TypeScript, Go, and Rust for
                                command-line tools
                            </li>
                            <li>Rust for performance-critical applications</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">
                            Web Development
                        </h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
                            <li>
                                <a
                                    href="https://astro.build"
                                    target="_blank"
                                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                    class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                                    >Astro</a
                                > for static sites and content-focused
                                applications
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <a
                                    href="https://react.dev"
                                    target="_blank"
                                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                    class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                                    >React</a
                                > for interactive web applications and
                                teaching
                            </li>
                            <li><a
                                    href="https://tailwindcss.com"
                                    target="_blank"
                                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                    class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                                    >Tailwind CSS</a
                                > for styling</li>
                            <li>
                                <a
                                    href="https://bun.sh"
                                    target="_blank"
                                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                    class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                                    >Bun</a
                                > as the preferred JavaScript runtime and
                                package manager
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">
                            Deployment & Infrastructure
                        </h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
                            <li><a
                                    href="https://vercel.com/"
                                    target="_blank"
                                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                    class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                                    >Vercel</a
                                > - Frontend cloud platform with instant deployments</li>
                            <li><a
                                    href="https://www.cloudflare.com/"
                                    target="_blank"
                                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                    class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                                    >Cloudflare</a
                                > - Edge network and web infrastructure</li>
                            <li><a
                                    href="https://www.digitalocean.com/"
                                    target="_blank"
                                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                    class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                                    >Digital Ocean</a
                                > - Cloud infrastructure for servers and databases</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
                    See my <a href="/uses" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline">uses page</a> for the development tools, productivity apps, and other software I rely on.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Areas of Interest</h2>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                    <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-lg">
                        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">
                            Language Models & AI Research
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-sm">
                            As I've increasingly engaged with and <a
                                href="/software#llm-tools"
                                class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                                >built tools for LLMs</a
                            >, I've become fascinated by understanding how they
                            work under the hood. This curiosity about their
                            architecture and capabilities is driving me to make
                            this a primary research focus in graduate school
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-lg">
                        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">
                            Creative & Interactive Systems
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-sm">
                            Building software and hardware systems that enable <a
                                href="/art"
                                class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                                >artistic expression</a
                            >, creative exploration, and tangible interactive
                            experiences through <a
                                href="/topics/physical-computing"
                                class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                                >physical computing</a
                            > and <a
                                href="/topics/p5js"
                                class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                                >creative coding</a
                            >
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-lg">
                        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">
                            Language Learning Technology
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-sm">
                            Developing <a
                                href="/topics/language-learning"
                                class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                                >tools and systems</a
                            > to enhance language acquisition through interactive
                            applications and AI-powered learning aids
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-lg">
                        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Computer Education</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm">
                            Creating <a
                                href="/topics/computer-education"
                                class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                                >resources and tools</a
                            > for teaching programming and computational thinking
                            through hands-on, project-based learning with <a
                                href="https://processing.org/"
                                target="_blank"
                                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                                >Processing</a
                            >, <a
                                href="https://p5js.org/"
                                target="_blank"
                                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                                >p5.js</a
                            >, <a
                                href="https://www.arduino.cc/"
                                target="_blank"
                                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                                >Arduino</a
                            >, and <a
                                href="https://www.espressif.com/en/products/socs/esp32"
                                target="_blank"
                                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                                >ESP32</a
                            >
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Get in Touch</h2>
                <p>
                    I'm always interested in connecting with fellow developers,
                    educators, and makers. Feel free to reach out through my <a
                        href="/contact"
                        class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                        >contact page</a
                    >
                    or connect with me on <a
                        href="https://github.com/osteele"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                        class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                        >GitHub</a
                    >,
                    <a
                        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/osteele"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                        class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                        >LinkedIn</a
                    >, or <a
                        href="https://bsky.app/profile/osteele.com"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                        class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                        >Bluesky</a
                    >.
                </p>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
